@host=http://localhost:8080

### Create facility - success
POST {{host}}/facilities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "facilityType": "MURABAHA",
  "principal": 500000.00,
  "profitRate": 8.5
}

### Create facility - nonexistent customer
POST {{host}}/facilities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 999,
  "facilityType": "MURABAHA",
  "principal": 500000.00,
  "profitRate": 8.5
}

### Approve facility (PENDING -> APPROVED)
PATCH {{host}}/facilities/3/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "APPROVED" }

### Illegal transition (APPROVED -> CLOSED, skipping ACTIVE)
PATCH {{host}}/facilities/3/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "CLOSED" }

### Activate facility (APPROVED -> ACTIVE)
PATCH {{host}}/facilities/2/status
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "ACTIVE" }

### Get facility by id
GET {{host}}/facilities/1

### Get facilities by customer
GET {{host}}/facilities?customerId=1
